com.reactivecascade.i.functional

Interface IRunnableAltFuture<IN,OUT>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IAltFuture<IN,OUT>, ICancellable, java.lang.Runnable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AltFuture

    public interface IRunnableAltFuture<IN,OUT>
extends IAltFuture<IN,OUT>, java.lang.Runnable
    Some implementations such as SettableAltFuture are not themselves runnable in their IThreadType's ExecutorService. Other, such as AltFuture are, and they are marked with this interface.
